{
  "stem": "20035.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And these troops were-- well, what I know now, I didn't know it then, that this was the second camp what they liberated in two days.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the previous day, they liberated another camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Think about it, that here are guys taking off their clothes, their shoes, handing out packages, handing out cans, handing out whatever they had, trying to do their other human.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if they would have known that any one of them who were unlucky enough by the goodness of these people that they had a sandwich, that sandwich killed that person whom they liberated.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The body could not take the calories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was lying on top of three packs of what they call k-rations.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "K-rations basically are-- even I understand exist American army, the box which has 6,000, 7,000 calorie of food in it, which is wrapped in a brown paper.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know it today by heart, with wax all around it, that in case if it falls into the water, even that the American soldier is able to open it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't have the strength to do anything else but lie-- but really lay on top of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's the reason why I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "These guys left within 10 minutes after.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I know that I had a pair of shoe and a pair of pants from one of the guys.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Suddenly the next troop came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the next troop looked to me like men from the Mars, or men from somewhere outer space.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We realized that they are Americans because they are wearing a similar uniform and they had a armband with the Red Cross on it.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
